metadata.name: SCREAM
metadata.description:
When you don't have a voice, you have to scream somehow.

7000 x 8500

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists.

Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
June 2-8, 2023.
